General.Name: Excelerate Energy Inc
General.Description: Excelerate Energy, Inc. provides liquefied natural gas (LNG) solutions worldwide. It offers regasification services, including floating storage and regasification units, infrastructure development, and LNG and natural gas supply. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in The Woodlands, Texas. Excelerate Energy, Inc. is a subsidiary of Excelerate Energy Holdings, LLC.
